352
00:25:50,799 --> 00:25:51,633
Dad.

353
00:25:53,301 --> 00:25:54,177
Yes.

354
00:25:55,595 --> 00:25:58,723
Please take good care
of Un-gyu and my wife for me.

355
00:26:03,561 --> 00:26:05,021
