00:30:12,852 --> 00:30:14,562
Hey. Have you eaten yet?

418
00:30:14,771 --> 00:30:16,439
No, not yet. What about you?

419
00:30:16,689 --> 00:30:19,818
Well, you know what my answer will be.
Let's go.

420
00:30:20,318 --> 00:30:21,861
